Despite Swansea manager Garry Monk saying he was unaware of offers. Sportsmail understands a first bid went in on January 6 and a second this week for £9.3m. 

Gomis has interest from Germany too.

Palace have also had a £3.5million bid for Swansea left-back Neil Taylor rejected.

